---
title: Roast Chickpea & Broccoli Super Salad with Avocado & Herby Mayonnaise
description: Get your greens in with this loaded salad! Crispy roasted chickpeas and broccoli add lots of crunchy texture to this meal, plus
avocado and a herby mayo for creamy richness. Toss it all together and dive in.

